    o kama pona tawa musi Veloren. jan li awen pali e musi ni.

    sina wile musi la, o sona e ni:

    - musi ni li pini ala a. ona li jo e pakala, e ijo pi pini ala, e nasin nasa, e ijo pi lon ala.

    - sina wile toki e pilin anu pakala la, o toki tawa mi lon lipu GitLab anu kulupu Discord anu kulupu Matrix.

    - musi Veloren la insa li open. sina ken musi, li ken ante, li ken pana e musi ni kepeken nasin GNU General Public License nanpa 3.

    - musi Veloren li wile ala e mani, li pali tan jan ale. jan pali ale li kama ala jo e mani.
    musi ni li pona tawa sina la, o kama lon kulupu pali mi a!

    sina lukin e toki ni la sina pona a. o musi pona a!

    ~ kulupu pali
